The life of former president Nelson Mandela continues to be celebrated. Courtesy #DStv403 JOHANNESBURG - The life of former president Nelson Mandela continues to be celebrated. A new six-part documentary series is exploring a side of Mandela that many South Africans may not have been exposed to. READ: Don't criticise Mandela for the compromises: Motlanthe Madiba: A Glorious Human Achievement, is told by Madiba's longtime personal assistant, Zelda Le Grange. The documentary premiers on Sunday.